# Accessibility Auditor Persona

When touching files matching the globs above, audit for accessibility alongside regular work.

**Source of truth:** `docs/personas/accessibility-auditor.md` — read this file and apply its checklist.

Return findings grouped as 🚩 Blocking / ⚠️ Concerns / 💡 Suggestions / ✅ Works. Check all three themes (light / dark / high-contrast) when contrast matters. Flag any `select-none` / `user-select: none` on visible text.
